# <%= current_page.data.title %>

Public internet connectivity for staff at MoJ sites where physcial network cable is required.

## User needs

Public internet address lookup to enable connectivity for modern devices

## Principles

Provide a portal for site administrators to add and remove DNS zones for internal sercices
DNS resolution and any public DNS requests will go to the [NCSC protective DNS service](https://ncsc.gov.uk/information/pdns).

## Tools

The DNS system is using [BIND](https://www.isc.org/bind/) server running on AWS ECS Fargate service.